---
# Conservative starting set; tighten as the codebase grows.
Checks: >
  -*,
  bugprone-*,
  performance-*,
  modernize-*,
  readability-*,
  -modernize-use-trailing-return-type,
  -readability-magic-numbers,
  -readability-identifier-length
WarningsAsErrors: ''
HeaderFilterRegex: '^src/'
FormatStyle: file
...
